SUMMARY:Tempo Run — 28 min
DESCRIPTION:Warmup: 5 min (zone1) — Easy jog\, build to a comfortable str
 ide.\nWork: 18 min (zone3) — Comfortably hard — controlled breathing\,
  sustainable effort.\nCooldown: 5 min (zone1) — Slow jog then walk. Let 
