BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260513
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260514
SUMMARY:Easy Run — 30 min
DESCRIPTION:Warmup: 5 min (zone1) — Easy walk or very light jog — just 
 get the blood moving.\nWork: 20 min (zone2) — Conversational pace. You s
 hould be able to speak in full sentences.\nCooldown: 5 min (zone1) — Slo
 w to a walk\, let heart rate drop naturally.\nWeek 2\, Run A (base plan 
 — adjusts on workout day)
UID:run-coach-2026-05-13@runcoach
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260516
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260517
SUMMARY:Intervals — 2×800 m
DESCRIPTION:Warmup: 5 min (zone1) — Easy jog to loosen up.\nInterval 1: 8
 00 m (zone4) — Hard but controlled — you should finish feeling like yo
 u have one more in you.\nRest: 0.5 min (rest) — 30 seconds — walk or s
 tand\, shake it out.\nInterval 2: 800 m (zone4) — Match the effort of in
 terval 1.\nCooldown: 5 min (zone1) — Easy jog then walk until fully reco
 vered.\nWeek 2\, Run B (base plan — adjusts on workout day)
UID:run-coach-2026-05-16@runcoach
END:VEVENT
